Samuel Page https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Samuel_Page 0 Samuel Page (born Samuel L. Elliott; November 5, 1976) is an American actor. He has appeared on popular television shows, such as Mad Men, Desperate Housewives, House of Cards, Switched at Birth, Scandal, Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt and Gossip Girl.
